    "Under Condition 2, V ‹ Π \" V πRLHF r ‹ ě V πDPO r ‹, and there exists an environment s.t.V πRLHF r ‹ ą V πDPO r ‹.Furthermore, we show that online DPO cannot close this gap, even when equipped with PILAF sampler.",
    "A numerical proof is deferred to Section B.8.Proposition 4.",
    "Under Condition 2, V πRLHF r ‹ ě V π online DPO r ‹, and there exists an environment s.t.V πRLHF r ‹ ą V π online DPO r ‹ \" V πDPO r ‹where the online sampler is PILAF sampler (Definition 1).",
    "Our key insight is that a strict performance gap between RLHF and DPO can exist under policy model mis-specification, and importantly, even sophisticated samplers like PILAF may fail to close the gap, an important nuance that, to our knowledge, has been overlooked in prior studies."
